Come home to Hunters Glen and you'll find well-equipped kitchens, mini blinds and full-size washer dryer in every apartment. There are private balconies and patios, and some apartments have vaulted ceilings. A fireplace is optional as well. Garages are available for a monthly charge. No wonder Hunters Glen is the ideal location for those who want the best of everything.
